\p{Let #{\mathfrak{g}} be a [Lie algebra](rs-001S). Then the \em{adjoint
representation} of #{\mathfrak{g}} is ##{\mathrm{ad}: \mathfrak{g} \to
\mathfrak{gl}({\mathfrak{g}})\\x \mapsto [x,-].}}
